name 'computer-systems-lesson5-level2a_v2-2025'
title 'Realistic Scenario'
description ''
question 'Which of the problems in the simulation seemed most similar to something you have experienced with a computer or device in real life?'
right 'Slow Performance (e.g., when your computer takes forever to load something)'
right 'Program Crashes (e.g., when an app suddenly closes while you are using it)'
right 'Error Messages (e.g., when a message pops up saying "File not found" or "Network error")'
right 'Permission Errors (e.g., when your computer says, "You do not have permission to open this file")'
allow_multiple_attempts false
